+Simple Crypto Calculator — App Description
+
+Create a simple mini app called “Simple Crypto Calculator”.
+The app allows users to calculate basic crypto values manually, such as total cost or holdings, without connecting to any external data sources.
+
+Core Features
+ 1. A text input field for entering the token name (optional for labeling).
+ 2. A numeric input field for quantity (number of tokens).
+ 3. A numeric input field for price per token (manual input).
+ 4. A button “Calculate” that multiplies quantity × price and displays the result.
+ 5. A display area showing the total value of the tokens.
+ 6. Optional: Allow multiple calculations in a list format, showing previous results with token name, quantity, price, and total.
+
+How the App Should Work
+ • User enters the quantity and price per token.
+ • Presses “Calculate”.
+ • The app immediately displays the total value.
+ • Users can repeat with different tokens or quantities.
+ • If multiple entries are supported, users can remove or clear items manually.
+ • All calculations are done locally; no internet or external data is used.
+
+UI Requirements
+ • Simple, clean form layout at the top for inputs.
+ • “Calculate” button clearly visible.
+ • Result displayed prominently below the form.
+ • Optional list of past calculations below result.
+ • No external API calls, no Web3, no internet required.
+
+Goal of the App
+
+Provide users with a quick, offline tool to calculate token totals and basic crypto math without any dependencies.
+```
+
